Package: gridmapR
Type: Package
Title: Creates a SF Grid Map based on a sf_polygon File
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Lars Kroll
Maintainer: The package maintainer <mail@lkroll.de>
Description: This packes takes an sf file and creates an optimal 
    hex stile representation of this map. The display is optimized 
    to show each area equally large while preserving the outer 
    geometry.
